reviewText: It was terrible.  Don't waste your time watching it.
I wanted to buy a movie I watched years ago and thought the name was the wanderers. This wasn't the movie I expected but it was Ok and no ones fault but mine I had the name wrong.

I didn't have any idea what to expect from this film - wasn't disappointed.  It has its flaws but everything has flaws, this was a fun bit of theater with clever dialog and even if the story didn't break any shocking new ground I didn't see the end coming a mile away either so that was cool.
This was beautifully done on a low budget. Parts of it were filmed around where I grew up . Awsome

I came across this movie that was recommended by a friend.  The trailer looked interesting...and the filmed delivered.  Very well acted and directed, from what clearly seems like a lower budget film.  I was surprised to hear this was the first film for the director.  Highly recommended.
